Policy,Snapshots,is,a,whitehouse,gov,feature,spotlighting,President,Obama,s,policies,Each,spotlight,focuses,on,a,particular,subject,and,is,composed,of,two,sections,Progress,which,gives,a,quick,overview,of,the,work,done,thus,far,by,the,administration,and,What,s,Next,which,illuminates,the,President,s,plans,for,continuing,progress,The,Policy,Snapshots,API,provides,a,customizable,JSON,feed,supplying,content,from,the,Policy,Snapshots,Content,can,be,accessed,by,specified,section,or,category,tags,Access,requires,no,account,or,authentication